name: MONOGRAM BOX LOGO TEE
description: The Supreme x Louis Vuitton SS ’17 collection featured a range of apparel, footwear, jewelry and accessories, and miscellaneous items – none bearing a more recognizable than this tee featuring the NYC brand’s famed Box Logo. Here, we see a clean, premium white tee sporting the Box Logo in red, with LV monogram co-branding appearing throughout.

name: THE 10: NIKE AIR FORCE 1 LOW
description: The Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Low “Volt” came out in December 2018 and added a blast of color to a year of releases from Virgil Abloh and the Swoosh.

name: YEEZY BOOST 350 V2
description: The YEEZY BOOST 350 V2 features an upper composed of re-engineered Primeknit. The post-dyed monofilament side stripe is woven into the upper.

name: AIR FORCE 1 LOW
description: The Nike Air Force 1 Low “Orange Skeleton” for Halloween 2020 is a spooky and festive release of the iconic lifestyle silhouette by Nike.

name: DONDA TWO LAYER LONG SLEEVE TE
description: The Kanye West Donda Two-Layer Long Sleeve Tee is co-created with Balenciaga Creative Director, Denma Gvasalia.

name: AIR JORDAN 1 RETRO HIGH
description: The special AJ1 is made entirely in Italy featuring a mixture of white and Dior Gray leather, with an Oblique monogrammed Swoosh (similar in style to the graphic featured on the fashion house's popular B23 high-top sneaker) and hand-painted edges.
